Write the clone method in the NurbsCurve class.
Remember to respond with a snippet in the form of the following:
```
class NurbsCurve {
    clone() {
        // your code here
    }
}
```

```javascript
class NurbsCurve {
    clone() {
        const clonedControlPoints = this.controlPoints.map(cp => cp.slice());
        return new NurbsCurve(this.knotVector.slice(), clonedControlPoints, this.degree, this.dimension);
    }
}
```
